channel.title: If you're IP banned what does it say?
channel.description: [b]Hi, I have a question. If someone is IP banned does it say "No responce from server Please try using a different world." Or does it say something different? If so apparentley I was IP banned for saying I don't like to see people cuss. o.O Thanks.[/b]

item.title: If you're IP banned what does it say?
